text: Chauvetia gigantea is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==Description== ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off Senegal. ==References== * Oliver J.D. & Rolan E. 2008. Las especies del género Chauvetia (Gastropoda, Neogastropoda) del área de Dakar, Senegal, África occidental, con la descripción de diez especies nuevas. Iberus 26(2) : 133-175 ==External links== * Category:Buccinidae Category:Gastropods described in 2008
title: Chauvetia gigantea
